Interface ReadableGraph<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Graph<T>, GraphView<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicGraph

    public interface ReadableGraph<T>
    Super-interface for any graph that has basic readable properties and query methods.
